Mills, CalCCA – Director of Data Analytics; and Matthew H. Langer, Clean Power Alliance, Chief Operating Officer and Yuliya Shmidt, Interim Advisor to Commissioner Karen Douglas.  CalCCA provided a presentation on 2023 Resource Adequacy (RA) market dynamics and compliance. This presentation included CalCCA’s analysis of the 2023 RA resource stack, indicating razor thin supply margins, and a discussion of potential contributing factors. CalCCA also made the following recommendations: (1) aligning consequences for non-compliance commensurate with load-serving entity conduct, (2) modifying the bidding requirements for RA imports to aide in increasing available RA supply, (3) increasing transparency of RA data, and (4) reconsidering the residual central procurement entity framework.  Discussion included the Resource Adequacy, Compliance and Market Dynamics, February 9, 2023, attached hereto as Attachment A.
